  "title": "Chef-De-Partie | 厨师",
  "description": "<h2><u><strong>Job Description | 职位说明</strong></u></h2>\n<h3><strong>1. Food Preparation &amp; Cooking | 食品准备与烹饪</strong></h3>\n<p>Prepare and cook a variety of Western dishes according to the menu requirements, including appetizers, main courses, and desserts.<br>\n根据菜单要求，准备并烹饪各种西式菜肴，包括前菜、主菜和甜点等。</p>\n<h3><strong>2. Ingredient Management | 食材与库存管理</strong></h3>\n<p>Manage ingredient usage and inventory efficiently to minimize waste and control food costs.<br>\n负责合理控制食材使用与库存，最大限度地减少浪费与成本。</p>\n<h3><strong>3. Equipment Maintenance | 设备维护与保养</strong></h3>\n<p>Maintain cleanliness and ensure proper functioning of all kitchen equipment and tools.<br>\n保持厨房设备及工具的清洁与维护，确保其正常、安全运行。</p>\n<h3><strong>4. Food Safety &amp; Hygiene | 食品安全与卫生</strong></h3>\n<p>Comply with food safety and hygiene standards to ensure all dishes meet quality and sanitation requirements.<br>\n严格遵守食品安全与卫生标准，确保所有菜品符合质量与卫生要求。</p>\n<h3><strong>5. Team Collaboration | 团队协作</strong></h3>\n<p>Work closely with fellow chefs and service staff to ensure timely delivery of dishes and an outstanding dining experience.<br>\n与其他厨师及服务团队紧密合作，确保菜品及时出餐并提供优质的用餐体验。</p>\n<h2><strong>Job Requirements | 任职要求</strong></h2>\n<p><strong>Education Level | 学历要求</strong><br>\nNo specific requirement  |  不限</p>\n<p><strong>Work Experience | 工作经验</strong><br>\nPrior experience preferred  |  有工作经验者优先</p>\n<p><strong>Job Skills | 工作技能</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Possess relevant Western cuisine cooking experience, including hot or cold dishes.<br>\n具备西餐烹饪经验，包括热菜或冷菜的制作。</li>\n  <li>Familiar with kitchen equipment operation and maintenance, ensuring safe and efficient use.<br>\n熟悉厨房设备的使用与维护，确保操作安全高效。</li>\n  <li>Strong teamwork spirit; able to collaborate effectively with other chefs and kitchen staff.<br>\n具备良好的团队合作意识，能与厨师及厨房人员紧密协作。</li>\n  <li>Adhere to food safety and hygiene regulations with understanding of standard operating procedures.<br>\n遵守食品安全与卫生标准，了解相关法规与操作流程。</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>Join Our Team | 加入我们</strong></h3>\n<p>We’re looking for <strong>passionate and energetic culinary talents</strong> who love creating beautiful food experiences with a professional team.<br>\n我们正在寻找<strong>有热情、有活力的厨师伙伴</strong>，与我们一起打造精致、美味的用餐体验。 🌸</p>",
