    "description": "<p>Founded in 2015, Tomacado is a premium lifestyle restaurant brand group that upholds the philosophy of “natural, healthy, beautiful, and sustainable” living. Starting with a combination of restaurant and flower shop, Tomacado pioneered a new business model that blends floral aesthetics with dining. Adhering to the design principle of “a unique style for each location” and featuring borderless fusion cuisine, Tomacado has established 13 integrated floral aesthetic dining spaces “blooming freely in the wilderness” in major cities including Beijing, Shanghai, Hangzhou, Shenzhen, Nanjing, and Hong Kong.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>花厨创立于2015年，践行“ 自然、健康、美好、可持续” 理念的品质生活方式品牌集团。以餐厅+花店开始，开创了花艺美学+餐饮新业态。秉持一店一色的体验设 计理念，以无国界融合菜为特色，花厨已在北京、上海、杭州、深圳、南京、香港等一线城市打造了13家“ 如花在野” 的复合式花艺美学餐饮体验空间。</p>",
